Eunice Jepkorir Kertich (amụrụ na 17 Febụwarị na afọ 1982) bụ onye Kenya na-agba ọsọ ogologo oge nke na-ahụ maka steeplechase
Ọ bụ onye nwetara ọlaọcha nke 2008 Olympic na ihe omume ahụ na onye nwetara ọla nchara na 2007 World Championships in Athletics
Nne na nna ya bụ ndị ọrụ ugbo ma o nwere ụmụnne asatọ (ụmụnne anọ na ụmụnne nwanyị anọ)
Ọ malitere ịgba ọsọ mgbe ọ dị afọ iri na ise mgbe ọ nọ n'ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị
N'afọ 2003, o sonyere na asọmpi ụfọdụ n'okporo ụzọ na Germany.
Ọ bụ onye nke asaa na ogologo ọsọ na 2004 World Cross Country Championships, ebe ndị otu Kenya, nke Jepkorir so na ya, meriri ọlaọcha na asọmpi otu
O meriri Parelloop 10K na asọmpi na Netherlands n'afọ 2005. Ọ mechara nke iri na anọ na 2006 World Road Running Championships, nyere ndị otu Kenya aka imeri asọmpi otu ahụ
O meriri na afọ 2007 Cross Internacional de la Constitución

O meriri ihe ndekọ steeplechase nke Kenya na 3000m na egwuregwu Bislett na Oslo na 15 na onwa isii, na afọ 2007 site na ịgba ọsọ 9:19.44. Izu abụọ ka e mesịrị, na 2 Julaị na afo 2007 na Athens ọ gbara ọsọ 9:14.52, nke bụ ndekọ Afrịka na Commonwealth.  Ihe ndekọ Afrịka gara aga (9:15.04) bụ nke Dorcus Inzikuru nke Uganda.
Na 2007 World Championships, ọ meriri ọla nchara na 3000 m steeplechase
Ọ meriri na afọ 2007 Cursa de Bombers 10K race na Barcelona ma gbachitere aha ya n'afọ sochirinụ.

N'abalị iri na anọ n'ọnwa Juun afọ 2008, ọ meziwanyere ihe ndekọ Afrịka ya ruo 9:11.18 na Huelva, Spain. Na afọ 2008 Summer Olympics ọ meriri ọlaọcha site na ịgba ọsọ 9:07.41, si otú a na-edozi ndekọ ọhụrụ nke Africa ọzọ
O rughị eru maka 2009 World Championships in Athletics.

Ọ bịara nke abụọ n'azụ Nuria Fernández na afọ 2011 Cross de San Sebastián na Jenụwarị, ebe di ya weere nsọpụrụ ụmụ nwoke. Ọ gbara naanị otu ugboro n'okporo ụzọ n'afọ ahụ, merie na Cáceres na onwa June
O meghị nke ọma na afọ 2012 Kenyan Olympic trials, na-agwụcha ọsọ ahụ na 10:13.28 nkeji ma na-efu ndị otu Olympic n'ihi ya.
Ọ lụrụ Josphat Kiprono Menjo, onye ọzọ na-agba ọsọ Kenya.
